parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the motorcycle to lose power, stall, or shut off while driving, which can lead to accidents or leave the rider stranded.
symptoms: the engine shuts off as if the ignition was shut off
the ignition switch comes apart or breaks inside.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Delayed or Unavailable Recall Repairs for Ignition Switch
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The lack of available parts for recall repairs can leave the motorcycle in an unsafe condition, putting the rider at risk of accidents or strandings.
symptoms: part has not been available for an extended period
dealership does not have parts available
dealership is unsure when parts will become available.
